    <section class="dac-hero-distribute">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="cols">
          <div class="col-6of12 col-push-6of12 dac-hero-distribute-figure">
            <img src="/distribute/images/heroes/about-google-play.svg" alt/>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6of12 col-pull-6of12 dac-hero-distribute-content-short">
            <h1>Google Play 商店简介</h1>
            <p>了解 Google Play 的功能如何帮助您让用户发现您的应用、通过应用获利以及扩大受众群体规模。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

